ESSENCE' 1.0
letting AMOUNT_QUEENS be domain int(1..n)
find queens : matrix indexed by [ AMOUNT_QUEENS ] of AMOUNT_QUEENS
such that   (alldifferent(queens)) 
            /\  
            (forall i,j : AMOUNT_QUEENS . 
                (i != j) /\
                 (-i + queens[i] != -j + queens[j]) /\
                 (queens[i] + i != queens[j] + j) )